data.description: 3bedroom, 1.5 bath cape cod in Struthers Schools. Walking in you will notice newer laminate floors stretching from the living room into the kitchen. Two first floor bedrooms with restored hardwood floors and decent closet space, carpeted third bedroom upstairs in the finished cape. The kitchen boasts updated white shaker cabinets, stone counter tops, and a dishwasher, refrigerator, and electric range that stay. Detached one car garage with concrete drive. High efficiency gas furnace with central air. Includes a double lot for a nicely sized yard.
